---
import Layout from '../components/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout title="Syn924 — Terms of Service">
  <article class="tos">
    <h1>Terms of Service</h1>
    <p class="sub">By commissioning me, you agree to the following. It's not legal jargon — just how I work.</p>

    <section>
      <h2>1. Payment</h2>
      <p>50% upon sketch completion, 50% upon completion.</p>
    </section>

    <section>
      <h2>2. Revisions</h2>
      <p>
        I do revisions during the sketch phase. Once we're in the middle/final
        stage, small changes are free. If I made a mistake interpreting your
        information, I'll fix it at no charge. If the change is due to missing
        information from you, there's a small extra charge ($2–5).
      </p>
    </section>

    <section>
      <h2>3. Timeline</h2>
      <p>
        Depending on the commission, turnaround ranges from three days to a week
        or two. Real life can cause delays — please understand.
      </p>
    </section>

    <section>
      <h2>4. Usage</h2>
      <p>Personal use is included. Commercial use adds $10.</p>
    </section>

    <section>
      <h2>5. Refunds</h2>
      <p>
        Refunds only if the artwork hasn't reached the color/render phase and
        I've taken excessively long (3+ weeks).
      </p>
    </section>

    <p class="closing">
      Anything not covered here can be discussed in person — just ask.
    </p>

    <a href="/" class="back">&larr; Back to gallery</a>
  </article>
</Layout>

<style>
  .tos {
    max-width: 680px;
    margin: 0 auto;
    padding: 48px 24px;
  }

  h1 {
    font-size: 1.6rem;
    color: var(--accent-gold);
    margin-bottom: 4px;
  }

  .sub {
    color: var(--text-secondary);
    font-size: 0.9rem;
    margin-bottom: 32px;
  }

  section {
    margin-bottom: 28px;
  }

  section h2 {
    font-size: 1rem;
    color: var(--accent-purple);
    text-transform: uppercase;
    letter-spacing: 0.06em;
    margin-bottom: 6px;
  }

  section p {
    color: var(--text-secondary);
    font-size: 0.95rem;
    line-height: 1.7;
  }

  .closing {
    color: var(--text-secondary);
    font-style: italic;
    margin: 32px 0 16px;
    font-size: 0.9rem;
  }

  .back {
    display: inline-block;
    margin-top: 8px;
    font-size: 0.9rem;
  }

  @media (max-width: 768px) {
    .tos {
      padding: 32px 16px;
    }
  }
</style>
